{"tid":1665800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚深水埗班警察為街坊帶嚟好多歡樂","createTime":"2019-10-20T16:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T17:36:14.000Z","uid":191462,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"48e79e5c15bcb03e538e3f67e99de8633947c7b4","tid":1665800,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"成隊警車懶係型響晒號着晒燈<br />\n以為U turn正面返嚟落車列陣<br />\n可以嚇走一眾街坊<br />\n點知全部街坊喺佢哋U返嚟時過晒對面馬路<br />\n睇佢哋U咗幾次又落地又上車<br />\n街坊就兩面馬路走<br />\n你U turn我哋就去對面<br />\n真係笑撚死人<br />\n<br />\n之後返到狗屋<br />\n街坊企晒喺對面睇佢哋做乜7<br />\n又發脾氣亂射幾粒催淚彈<br />\n又開咪話有人衝擊警署同扔汽油彈<br />\n之後水炮車入屋前發脾氣亂9咁向途人記者射水<br />\n但其實乜示威者都冇 <br />\n石仔都冇粒有人扔過<br />\n<br />\n其實佢哋呢排係咪真係撞鬼？"},{"pid":"1bc75100b43024b4a765a79b5b0ceca38f13265e","tid":1665800,"uid":57433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:45:11.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0c7148d3f3fc2b0522237762d84d95ad3b2fd6","tid":1665800,"uid":325346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:48:10.000Z","msg":"有旅遊巴入左警署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053e6dacc9713b433cf3d14aa3c48623c51c0853","tid":1665800,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e0c7148d3f3fc2b0522237762d84d95ad3b2fd6","tid":1665800,"uid":325346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:48:10.000Z","msg":"有旅遊巴入左警署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:49:30.000Z","msg":"消防車都入咗架"},{"pid":"58fe79fdfd7b16ae7332f974154aee16f76ab57d","tid":1665800,"uid":211727,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:49:37.000Z","msg":"班狗自己智障就惱羞成怒<br />\n小學雞EQ都高過佢哋<br />\n好心砍掉自己投胎重練啦<br />\n難聽啲講句 家下支持死黑警嘅都係廢老<br />\n老死病死晒之後咪又係得返我哋呢一代<br />\n想有好日子過？don't ff too much<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d64ec8327fb9fff48259942f18a5ffa0e2